  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have access to a special Transformation known as Corrupted Chakra Mode. As a Bonus Action, you can enter this form for the next minute. You gain the following benefits: </p><ul><li><p>You gain 30 feet of Tremorsense and while a creature is within your tremorsense you cannot be surprised by them. </p></li><li><p>You gain temporary hit points and chakra points equal to your level. </p></li><li><p>When you would deal poison damage, you deal extra damage equal to your proficiency bonus </p></li><li><p>You are immune to the slowed and weakened conditions.</p></li></ul>",
